            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"pt-BR\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>Ambitionz Rebirth</title>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover\">\n    <meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#050608\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Ambitionz Rebirth e uma plataforma TCG de fantasia sombria para duelar, colecionar e abrir boosters.\">\n    <link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/static/manifest.webmanifest\">\n    <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/static/icons/icon.svg\">\n    <link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/static/assets/rebirth/cards/dreadclaw-art.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/static/css/rebirth.css?v=v71_PRODUCT_READINESS-6\">\n</head>\n<body class=\"rb-page rb-home-page rb-landing-page\">\n    \n\n<header class=\"rb-global-nav\" data-rebirth-global-nav data-rebirth-wallet aria-label=\"Navegação global Ambitionz Rebirth\">\n    <a class=\"rb-brand rb-global-brand\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Ambitionz Rebirth início\">\n        <span>A</span>\n        <strong>Ambitionz Rebirth</strong>\n    </a>\n    <nav class=\"rb-global-tabs\" aria-label=\"Produtos Rebirth\">\n        <a href=\"/rebirth\" class=\"\">Arena</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/campaign\" class=\"\">Campanha</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/collection\" class=\"\">Coleção</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/shop\" class=\"\">Loja</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/progression\" class=\"\">Recompensas</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/profile\" class=\"\">Perfil</a>\n    </nav>\n    <section class=\"rb-global-player\" aria-label=\"Jogador e carteira\">\n        <div class=\"rb-global-identity\">\n            <span>Visitante</span>\n            <strong data-rebirth-username>Visitante</strong>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-global-xp\" aria-label=\"Nível e XP\">\n            <span>Nível 1</span>\n            <strong>0/500 XP</strong>\n            <i aria-hidden=\"true\"><b style=\"width: 0%\"></b></i>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-global-wallet\" aria-label=\"Carteira\">\n            <span>Ouro <strong data-rebirth-wallet-value=\"GOLD\">0</strong></span>\n            <span class=\"rb-coinz\">Gemas <strong data-rebirth-wallet-value=\"COINZ\">0</strong></span>\n        </div>\n        \n            <button class=\"rb-nav-auth\" type=\"button\" data-rebirth-auth-open>Entrar / Cadastrar</button>\n        \n    </section>\n</header>\n\n<div class=\"rb-auth-modal\" data-rebirth-auth-modal hidden>\n    <button class=\"rb-auth-backdrop\" type=\"button\" data-rebirth-auth-close aria-label=\"Fechar login\"></button>\n    <section class=\"rb-auth-dialog\" role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"rebirth-auth-title\">\n        <button class=\"rb-auth-close\" type=\"button\" data-rebirth-auth-close aria-label=\"Fechar\">x</button>\n        <div class=\"rb-auth-dialog-copy\">\n            <span>Ambitionz Rebirth</span>\n            <h2 id=\"rebirth-auth-title\">Entrar / Cadastrar</h2>\n            <p>Entre para guardar sua coleção, nível, Ouro e Gemas entre duelos.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-auth-modal-grid\">\n            <form class=\"rb-auth-form rb-auth-modal-form\" data-rebirth-login data-auth-redirect=\"/rebirth\">\n                <span>Entrar</span>\n                <label>Email<input name=\"email\" type=\"text\" inputmode=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" required></label>\n                <label>Senha<input name=\"password\" type=\"password\" autocomplete=\"current-password\" required></label>\n                <button class=\"rb-button-secondary rb-secondary\" type=\"submit\">Entrar</button>\n            </form>\n            <form class=\"rb-auth-form rb-auth-modal-form\" data-rebirth-register data-auth-redirect=\"/rebirth?firstRun=1\">\n                <span>Cadastrar</span>\n                <label>Jogador<input name=\"username\" autocomplete=\"username\" required minlength=\"3\"></label>\n                <label>Email<input name=\"email\" type=\"text\" inputmode=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" required></label>\n                <label>Senha<input name=\"password\" type=\"password\" autocomplete=\"new-password\" required minlength=\"8\"></label>\n                <button class=\"rb-button-primary rb-cta\" type=\"submit\">Criar conta</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-product-result rb-auth-modal-result\" data-rebirth-auth-result aria-live=\"polite\">Pronto.</div>\n    </section>\n</div>\n    <main class=\"rb-home-shell\">\n        <section id=\"rebirth-home-hero\" class=\"rb-home-hero\" aria-label=\"Produto Ambitionz Rebirth\">\n            <div class=\"rb-home-copy\">\n                <h1>Ambitionz Rebirth</h1>\n                <p class=\"rb-home-line\">Duelos, coleção e mercado em uma mesa viva.</p>\n                <p>Convoque monstros, combine duplicatas, evolua cartas incomuns e lute por recompensas de temporada.</p>\n                <p>Uma plataforma TCG de alta fantasia com economia em Ouro e Gemas.</p>\n                <div class=\"rb-home-actions\">\n                    <a class=\"rb-cta rb-cta-wide\" href=\"/rebirth\"><span>A</span> Entrar na Arena <i aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></a>\n                    <a class=\"rb-secondary\" href=\"/rebirth/collection\">Minha Coleção</a>\n                    <a class=\"rb-secondary\" href=\"/rebirth/shop\">Loja & Mercado</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"rb-home-proof\" aria-label=\"Pilares do produto\">\n                    <article><span>Arena</span><strong>Clash tático</strong></article>\n                    <article><span>Coleção</span><strong>100 cartas</strong></article>\n                    <article><span>Economia</span><strong>Ouro + Gemas</strong></article>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"rb-home-preview\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"rb-score-frame\">\n                    <div>\n                        <span>Você</span>\n                        <strong>30 HP</strong>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <span>Turno</span>\n                        <strong>01</strong>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <span>Bot</span>\n                        <strong>30 HP</strong>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <article class=\"rb-preview-card\">\n                    <div class=\"rb-card-art\" style=\"background-image: url('/static/assets/rebirth/cards/dreadclaw-art.webp')\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"rb-card-body\">\n                        <span>Fera - Nível 1</span>\n                        <strong>Dreadclaw</strong>\n                        <p>Escolha um monstro. Force uma resposta. Resolva um clash.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <b class=\"rb-power\">6</b>\n                </article>\n                <div class=\"rb-home-hand\">\n                    <span>2</span>\n                    <span>3</span>\n                    <span>4</span>\n                    <span>5</span>\n                    <span>6</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"rb-product-stats rb-home-status\" aria-label=\"Status Rebirth\">\n            \n                <article><span>Modo</span><strong>Clash TCG</strong></article>\n            \n                <article><span>Cartas</span><strong>100 no catálogo</strong></article>\n            \n                <article><span>Economia</span><strong>Ouro + Gemas</strong></article>\n            \n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"rb-product-grid rb-home-product-grid\" aria-label=\"Produto Rebirth\">\n            \n                <article class=\"rb-product-panel\">\n                    <span>Rebirth</span>\n                    <h2>Entrar na Arena</h2>\n                    <p>Comece um duelo contra o bot e leia a mesa viva em tempo real.</p>\n                    <a class=\"rb-secondary\" href=\"/rebirth\">Abrir</a>\n                </article>\n            \n                <article class=\"rb-product-panel\">\n                    <span>Rebirth</span>\n                    <h2>Minha Coleção</h2>\n                    <p>Monte um deck de 30 cartas com monstros, magias, armadilhas e evoluções.</p>\n                    <a class=\"rb-secondary\" href=\"/rebirth/collection\">Abrir</a>\n                </article>\n            \n                <article class=\"rb-product-panel\">\n                    <span>Rebirth</span>\n                    <h2>Loja &amp; Mercado</h2>\n                    <p>Abra boosters de 5 cartas e veja ofertas ativas de outros jogadores.</p>\n                    <a class=\"rb-secondary\" href=\"/rebirth/shop\">Abrir</a>\n                </article>\n            \n                <article class=\"rb-product-panel\">\n                    <span>Rebirth</span>\n                    <h2>Recompensas</h2>\n                    <p>Suba de nível com XP, missões diárias e marcos de temporada.</p>\n                    <a class=\"rb-secondary\" href=\"/rebirth/progression\">Abrir</a>\n                </article>\n            \n                <article class=\"rb-product-panel\">\n                    <span>Rebirth</span>\n                    <h2>Perfil</h2>\n                    <p>Acompanhe nível, selos, carteira e controles da conta.</p>\n                    <a class=\"rb-secondary\" href=\"/rebirth/profile\">Abrir</a>\n                </article>\n            \n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <script>\n        window.REBIRTH_CSRF = \"OUVc9RYUk7g4pR7vMH7L0h6cWwMiXhgGchL57geoEo8\";\n        window.REBIRTH_AUTH_ENDPOINTS = {\n            register: \"/api/rebirth/auth/register\",\n            login: \"/api/rebirth/auth/login\",\n            logout: \"/api/rebirth/auth/logout\",\n            wallet: \"/api/rebirth/wallet\"\n        };\n    </script>\n    <script src=\"/static/js/pwa.js?v=v71_PRODUCT_READINESS-6\"></script>\n    <script src=\"/static/js/rebirth_global.js?v=v71_PRODUCT_READINESS-6\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>"
