          ],
          "content": {
            "size": 9736,
            "mimeType": "text/html; charset=utf-8",
            "compression": 10444,
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"pt-BR\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>Loja &amp; Mercado - Ambitionz Rebirth</title>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover\">\n    <meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#050608\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Abra boosters, revele cartas por raridade e acompanhe ofertas do mercado.\">\n    <link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/static/manifest.webmanifest\">\n    <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/static/icons/icon.svg\">\n    <link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/static/assets/rebirth/cards/dreadclaw-art.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/static/css/rebirth.css?v=v71_PRODUCT_READINESS-6\">\n</head>\n<body class=\"rb-page rb-home-page rb-product-page\">\n    \n\n<header class=\"rb-global-nav\" data-rebirth-global-nav data-rebirth-wallet aria-label=\"Navegação global Ambitionz Rebirth\">\n    <a class=\"rb-brand rb-global-brand\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Ambitionz Rebirth início\">\n        <span>A</span>\n        <strong>Ambitionz Rebirth</strong>\n    </a>\n    <nav class=\"rb-global-tabs\" aria-label=\"Produtos Rebirth\">\n        <a href=\"/rebirth\" class=\"\">Arena</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/campaign\" class=\"\">Campanha</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/collection\" class=\"\">Coleção</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/shop\" class=\"is-active\">Loja</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/progression\" class=\"\">Recompensas</a>\n        <a href=\"/rebirth/profile\" class=\"\">Perfil</a>\n    </nav>\n    <section class=\"rb-global-player\" aria-label=\"Jogador e carteira\">\n        <div class=\"rb-global-identity\">\n            <span>Visitante</span>\n            <strong data-rebirth-username>Visitante</strong>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-global-xp\" aria-label=\"Nível e XP\">\n            <span>Nível 1</span>\n            <strong>0/500 XP</strong>\n            <i aria-hidden=\"true\"><b style=\"width: 0%\"></b></i>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-global-wallet\" aria-label=\"Carteira\">\n            <span>Ouro <strong data-rebirth-wallet-value=\"GOLD\">0</strong></span>\n            <span class=\"rb-coinz\">Gemas <strong data-rebirth-wallet-value=\"COINZ\">0</strong></span>\n        </div>\n        \n            <button class=\"rb-nav-auth\" type=\"button\" data-rebirth-auth-open>Entrar / Cadastrar</button>\n        \n    </section>\n</header>\n\n<div class=\"rb-auth-modal\" data-rebirth-auth-modal hidden>\n    <button class=\"rb-auth-backdrop\" type=\"button\" data-rebirth-auth-close aria-label=\"Fechar login\"></button>\n    <section class=\"rb-auth-dialog\" role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"rebirth-auth-title\">\n        <button class=\"rb-auth-close\" type=\"button\" data-rebirth-auth-close aria-label=\"Fechar\">x</button>\n        <div class=\"rb-auth-dialog-copy\">\n            <span>Ambitionz Rebirth</span>\n            <h2 id=\"rebirth-auth-title\">Entrar / Cadastrar</h2>\n            <p>Entre para guardar sua coleção, nível, Ouro e Gemas entre duelos.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-auth-modal-grid\">\n            <form class=\"rb-auth-form rb-auth-modal-form\" data-rebirth-login data-auth-redirect=\"/rebirth/shop\">\n                <span>Entrar</span>\n                <label>Email<input name=\"email\" type=\"text\" inputmode=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" required></label>\n                <label>Senha<input name=\"password\" type=\"password\" autocomplete=\"current-password\" required></label>\n                <button class=\"rb-button-secondary rb-secondary\" type=\"submit\">Entrar</button>\n            </form>\n            <form class=\"rb-auth-form rb-auth-modal-form\" data-rebirth-register data-auth-redirect=\"/rebirth?firstRun=1\">\n                <span>Cadastrar</span>\n                <label>Jogador<input name=\"username\" autocomplete=\"username\" required minlength=\"3\"></label>\n                <label>Email<input name=\"email\" type=\"text\" inputmode=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" required></label>\n                <label>Senha<input name=\"password\" type=\"password\" autocomplete=\"new-password\" required minlength=\"8\"></label>\n                <button class=\"rb-button-primary rb-cta\" type=\"submit\">Criar conta</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rb-product-result rb-auth-modal-result\" data-rebirth-auth-result aria-live=\"polite\">Pronto.</div>\n    </section>\n</div>\n    <main class=\"rb-home-shell rb-product-shell\" data-page-key=\"shop\">\n        <section class=\"rb-product-hero\" aria-label=\"Loja &amp; Mercado\">\n            <div>\n                <span class=\"rb-product-kicker\">Ambitionz Rebirth</span>\n                <h1>Loja &amp; Mercado</h1>\n                <p>Abra boosters, revele cartas por raridade e acompanhe ofertas do mercado.</p>\n            </div>\n            <a class=\"rb-cta rb-cta-wide\" href=\"/rebirth/shop\"><span>A</span> Abrir Booster <i aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></a>\n        </section>\n\n        \n            <section class=\"rb-shop-gacha\" aria-label=\"Gacha de boosters\">\n                <div class=\"rb-shop-gacha-copy\">\n                    <span>Gacha Rebirth</span>\n                    <h2>Pacote de 5 cartas</h2>\n                    <p>O backend sorteia 3 comuns e 2 incomuns antes da interface revelar o resultado.</p>\n                    <div class=\"rb-gacha-slots\" aria-label=\"Slots de raridade\">\n                        <span>Comum</span>\n                        <span>Comum</span>\n                        <span>Comum</span>\n                        <span>Incomum</span>\n                        <span>Incomum</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"rb-shop-pack-list\">\n                    \n                        <article class=\"rb-product-panel rb-shop-offer rb-shop-pack\">\n                            <s